
Processing Steps for Variables
variable = [aice, sst, u200, v200, z200, siextent]

    0.0 Download
    0.1 Monthly, Yearly, JJA
    0.2 Combine

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
siextent
    0.0 Download
        DO.0_aice_download_1990-2100
            wget downloads aice (monthly) from CESM2 to /cofast/lhoffman/cesmle/aice/raw
            runs 'D0_aice_year_mon_vX.py'
            deletes data in raw
            
    0.1 Monthly
        D0.1_aice_year_mon_vX.py 
            grab raw aice data file
            build arctic and antarctic mask (aice >= 0.15; lat >= 50 OR lat <= 50)
            calculate siextent (siextent = sum(aice*acello))
            save siextentn and siextents
                monthly: /cofast/lhoffman/cesmle/aice/siextent/BHISTcmip6_year_1001.001_siextent_199001-199912.nc
        
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
aice
    0.0 Download
        D0.0_aice_download_1990-2100
            wget downloads aice (monthly) from CESM2 to /cofast/lhoffman/cesmle/aice/raw
            runs 'D0_aice_year_mon_vX.py'
            deletes data in raw

    0.1 Monthly, Yearly
        D0.1_aice_year_mon_vX.py
            grab raw aice data file
            save aice_monthly:
                /cofast/lhoffman/cesmle/mon/
            build arctic and antarctic mask (aice >= 0.15; lat >= 50 OR lat <= 50)
            calcualte yearly mean aice for mask
            save aice_yearly_mean
                yearly: /cofast/lhoffman/cesmle/aice/year/

    0.2 Combine
        D0.2_aice_combine_year_1990-2100.py
            concatenates yearly mean aice to one dataset
            save aice: /cofast/lhoffman/cesmle/aice/year_combined/aice_cesmle_first50members_year_190001-210012.nc

    0.3 Monthly
        D0.3_aice_monthly.py 
            reads in mon_combined
            saves separate file for each month
                /cofast/lhoffman/cesmle/aice/mon/aice_cesmle_first50members_mon_JAN_199001-210012.nc
                /cofast/lhoffman/cesmle/aice/mon/aice_cesmle_last50members_mon_JAN_199001-210012.nc

    0.4 Re-grid (*** this makes the input to the CNN ***)
        D0.4_aice_regrid_JJA.py
            reads in:
                aice: /cofast/lhoffman/cesmle/aice/mon/aice_cesmle_first50members_mon_JAN_199001-210012.nc
                (lat,lon) aice: /cofast/lhoffman/cesmle/aice/raw/b.e21.BHISTcmip6.f09_g17.LE2-1001.001.cice.h.aice.185001-185912.nc
                (lat,lon) sst: /cofast/lhoffman/cesmle/z200/raw/b.e21.BHISTcmip6.f09_g17.LE2-1001.001.cam.h1.Z200.18500101-18591231.nc
            takes JJA mean
            uses scipy.interpolate griddata to regrid aice to sst griddata ; plots for verification
            saves re-gridded aice: /cofast/lhoffman/cesmle/cnn_slowdown/aice_regridded_sstgrid_JJA_1990-2100.nc
                
