sst

    0.0 Download
        D0.0_sst_download_1990-2100
            wget downloads sst (monthly) from CESM2 to /cofast/lhoffman/cesmle/sst/raw

        
    0.2 Combine
        D0.2_sst_combine_mon_1990-2100.py
            reads in raw data
            concatenates members and years
            saves: /cofast/lhoffman/cesmle/sst/mon_combined/sst_cesmle_first50members_mon_199001-210012.nc
                   /cofast/lhoffman/cesmle/sst/mon_combined/sst_cesmle_last50members_mon_199001-210012.nc
            
    0.3 Monthly
        D0.3_sst_monthly.py 
            reads in mon_combined
            saves separate file for each month
                /cofast/lhoffman/cesmle/sst/mon/sst_cesmle_first50members_mon_JAN_199001-210012.nc
                /cofast/lhoffman/cesmle/sst/mon/sst_cesmle_last50members_mon_JAN_199001-210012.nc
    
